# GCP Provider (Terraform)

Terraform Google Cloud provider configuration and usage.

Install:
```hcl
terraform {
  required_providers {
    google = { source = "hashicorp/google" version = "~> 4.0" }
  }
}
```

Quick example:
```hcl
provider "google" { project = "my-project" region = "us-central1" }
```